WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:02.341
I was only four years old

00:00:02.365 --> 00:00:05.276
when I saw my mother
load a washing machine

00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:07.482
for the very first time in her life.

00:00:07.943 --> 00:00:09.919
That was a great day for my mother.

00:00:10.431 --> 00:00:13.276
My mother and father
had been saving money for years

00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:15.340
to be able to buy that machine,

00:00:15.364 --> 00:00:17.410
and the first day it was going to be used,

00:00:17.434 --> 00:00:20.573
even Grandma was invited
to see the machine.

00:00:20.597 --> 00:00:21.733
(Laughter)

00:00:21.757 --> 00:00:24.276
And Grandma was even more excited.

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:28.600
Throughout her life, she had been
heating water with firewood,

00:00:28.624 --> 00:00:32.634
and she had hand-washed laundry
for seven children.